    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取材于我惨烈的失眠体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在夜晚打出各种卡牌来尽快入眠，在白天进行各种行动来强化卡组。调配卡组和备牌来构筑最棒的卡组，战胜失眠！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是一个单人Rougelike卡组构建游戏。玩家需要在夜晚通过消费时间打出卡牌来减少自己的清醒值。在夜晚过后的日间，玩家则可以消费体力来进行活动从而获得更多卡牌和各种增益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外还可以在深梦模式中挑战越来越困难的游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得各式各样的卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战胜失眠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行各种活动来帮助夜晚的睡眠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/444a683258d3914a7827a7f997af7ace.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/444a683258d3914a7827a7f997af7ace.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的卡组来完善战术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/35e66ba9b7320b39683badb3cb64f6eb.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/35e66ba9b7320b39683badb3cb64f6eb.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
